# formIntersection(_:)

**Instance Method**

Removes the contents of this range set that aren’t also in the given range set.

## Declaration

```swift
mutating func formIntersection(_ other: RangeSet<Bound>)
```

## Parameters

- **other**: A range set to intersect with.
